---
title: Beef Rump & Garlic-Peppercorn Butter with Garlicky Veggies & Mash
description: Simple and sensational – they're the buzzwords for tonight's dinner. A tender cut of beef rump with a punchy fragrant butter, cooked with garlic and peppercorns, fluffy mash and nutty veggies combine to make a special meal that'll have you buzzing too!
